snippet.title: Worshippers of Cthulhu Reveal Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Another world premiere trailer revealed Worshippers of Cthulhu, a Lovecraftian city-builder in which you manage a moody cult and uncover ancient secrets. It’s coming to PC in 2024.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow
